                <p/>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Aristodèmos fils de Dionysios.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Aristodemos son of Dionysios.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Aristodemos figlio di Dionysios.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>As such funerary urns are unusual in Cyrenaica and common at Alexandria, the purported Cyrenaican origin is rather doubtful.</p>
	<p/>
